    <section class="about-us-section">
      <h1 class="about-us-title">
        About Us
      </h1>
      <p class="about-us-text">
        Welcome to Namnam, your ultimate Restaurant / Store / Service Review Web Application. Our platform is dedicated to helping you discover the best places in and around the campus area. Whether you're a student or staff member, our goal is to provide you with honest and authentic reviews to make your choices easier.
      </p>
      <h2 class="features-title">
        Features:
      </h2>
      <ul class="features-list">
        <li>User-Friendly Interface: We believe in simplicity and ease of use, ensuring that our website is intuitive and easy to navigate.</li>
        <li>Authentic Reviews: All reviews on Namnam are written by real people who have personally experienced the establishments. We do not allow fake or paid reviews.</li>
        <li>Diverse Categories: Namnam covers a wide range of establishments, including restaurants, stores, and various services, catering to all your needs and preferences.</li>
        <li>Campus-Based: Our focus is on establishments in and around the campus area, making it convenient for you to explore nearby options.</li>
        <li>Detailed Listings: Each establishment featured on Namnam comes with comprehensive information, including contact details, operating hours, location, and a brief description.</li>
        <li>Ratings and Recommendations: Users can rate their experiences and leave recommendations to help others make informed choices.</li>
        <li>User Accounts: Creating an account on Namnam allows users to personalize their experience, bookmark favorite spots, and track their reviews and contributions.</li>
        <li>Community Engagement: We encourage community engagement through comments, likes, and sharing of reviews, fostering a vibrant and supportive community.</li>
        <li>Mobile App: To enhance accessibility, Namnam offers a mobile app for both Android and iOS users, enabling you to explore and review establishments on the go.</li>
        <li>Social Integration: Users can connect their Namnam profiles to their social media accounts, sharing their experiences with friends and family.</li>
      </ul>

